<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
        body {
            color: #000;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 640px;
            margin: auto;
        }
        .card {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            /* width: 640px; */
            height: 80%;
            /* margin: auto; */
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }        .image {
            padding-top: 50px;
            display: block;
        }
        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .wrapper {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            color: #000;
        }
        .decoration {
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .magic-link {
            color: white;
            background-color: blue;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .magic-link {
            width: auto;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        .color-black {
            color: #000;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #ddd; width: 100%">
    <div class="container">
        <%- include('./header.ejs') %>
            <hr style="margin:0" />
            <div class="card">
                <h4 class="color-black"><b>Greetings from Scaffold</b></h4>
                <h4 class="color-black">Dear <%= firstName %> ,</h4>
                <p class="color-black">We regret to inform you that your account has been deactivated on our website. This decision was made due to [reason for deactivation], which is in violation of our terms of service.</p>
                <div class="wrapper">
                    <p class="color-black">Please note that you will no longer be able to access your account, and any data associated with it has been permanently deleted. If you have any questions or concerns regarding this matter, please do not hesitate to contact us.</p>
                    <p class="color-black">Thank you for your understanding.</p>
                    <p class="color-black">Thank You</p>
                    <p class="color-black"><b>Scaffold team</b></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr style="margin:0" />
            <%- include('./footer.ejs') %>
    </div>
</body>

</html>